{"tid":1940701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter心理教學- 好多人唔明五毛係唔洗打","createTime":"2020-03-24T02:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T03:59:17.000Z","uid":19945,"like":166,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"6559597f6a7d9f3fac67d6bba3e61b77a16b94a4","tid":1940701,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"近期連登多左好多Twitter交流，<br />\n有唔少巴打表示唔夠EQ應五毛，<br />\n我用回覆過嘅說話幫幫大家平衡下心理，<br />\n從此展開開心釣五毛人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當訓練下，<br />\n教你點樣可以唔在意，<br />\n記住你嘅目的係打中國，<br />\n踩中國狗顯示佢地國家差嘅一面。<br />\n<br />\n1.佢地愈人身攻擊，人地愈同情你，愈覺得佢地過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.佢地講野其實好好笑，例如：最新我講話大陸突然無左成千萬電話。佢地覆我：poor HK cockroaches, only have 1 phone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.大部分人其實唔會睇reply的reply，佢愈鬧你愈推到你個reply上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n因為班小粉紅唔識用腦，<br />\n香港人打戰線係用自己作為Twitter User去發展，<br />\n真心想用又好 扮又好，<br />\n識得發展自己個account 唔會淨做政治嘢，<br />\n同埋香港人係用自身真實經歷去說服人，<br />\n小粉紅只會用佢地嘅：<br />\n- 0-10 follower<br />\n- 殘體字 bio page<br />\n- blank profile pic<br />\n- comment: Fuck you/ lick US ass/ cockroaches/ US dog/ White Pig/ your mother died<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且依家愈來愈多人用#WuMao，<br />\n大家要明美國就算多白左都係美國人，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人地民主社會用幾百年爭取同發展，<br />\n點會蠢到信你d假account，<br />\n所以我成日講打國際戰線，<br />\n愈多五毛愈好，Trump粉愈嬲，<br />\n中立派愈反感，Demo派愈幫唔落，<br />\n其實係connect緊美國全體反共</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家快d開Twitter釣五毛，<br />\n其實佢地鬧你嘅說話，<br />\n真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8be375d15558d7214da0e49be3866bf314ef37ee","tid":1940701,"uid":19945,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"所以回覆時，愈輕鬆愈好，<br />\n用佢d人身攻擊言論搞下笑，<br />\n多謝佢幫你推個reply上去比更多人睇，<br />\n多d tag#WuMao，講講下佢地就唔敢覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495bc5154c645f3c05a90b2f65447473fba39ef7","tid":1940701,"uid":94982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be375d15558d7214da0e49be3866bf314ef37ee","tid":1940701,"uid":19945,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"所以回覆時，愈輕鬆愈好，<br />\n用佢d人身攻擊言論搞下笑，<br />\n多謝佢幫你推個reply上去比更多人睇，<br />\n多d tag#WuMao，講講下佢地就唔敢覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"Agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕輕鬆鬆應對，唔係駛理d咩nmsl"},{"pid":"9732d836aa1d48d81678fe43073f65c591a7af42","tid":1940701,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c4d436abf305e0560bf03307d07db9f5361ca4","tid":1940701,"uid":2662,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"唔駛理佢哋，見到佢哋仇恨言論直接report<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd73d78bee09bc2698ea04509feef532a659d1","tid":1940701,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f95a55d6903e17f651cb6d9878ffa36c8a17381","tid":1940701,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"推，唔使同佢哋理論"},{"pid":"0838a0132b1cc506a95226e8cb879f7c4316043b","tid":1940701,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:12:03.000Z","msg"